Buzz Mobilizer Extension
https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/mghfmhkekcpknpgphanbgcjlekikmbln

Buzz Mobilizer wraps the excellent Buzz mobile site and allows it to be accessed in a Chrome Extension Popup. The Buzz mobile site can be accessed from your browser at: https://m.google.com/app/buzz?force=1 

There are two limitations that you should be aware of:
1) Links to user profiles fail.
2) Location services are unavailable.

Buzz me if you find this extension useful or have any suggestions.
http://buzz.google.com/dshaw7

